* {{flag|KOR}}[[世宗特別自治市|世宗特別自治市]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/news/community/2013/04/06/closer-ties-between-putrajaya-and-sejong-korea/|title=Closer ties between Putrajaya and Sejong, Korea - Community {{!}} The Star Online|last=Yeen|first=Oh Ing|access-date=2017-02-13|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103051705/http://www.thestar.com.my/news/community/2013/04/06/closer-ties-between-putrajaya-and-sejong-korea/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

